OL,3,CDerry house fire investigated as arson
OL,5,FPolice are investigating a house fire
OL,6,Fin Londonderry as arson with intent to
OL,7,Fendanger life.
OL,9,FIt happened in the Slaughtmanus Road
OL,10,Farea in the early hours of Thursday.
OL,12,FEmergency crews attended the scene and
OL,13,Fa man was taken to hospital for
OL,14,Ftreatment for the effects of smoke
OL,15,Finhalation.
OL,17,FPolice said "considerable" damage was
OL,18,Fcaused to the property.
