OL,3,CDerry house fire investigated as arson
OL,5,F"A male occupant in the property was
OL,6,Fasleep when he was alerted to the
OL,7,Fblaze by the sound of his smoke alarm
OL,8,Fand his dog barking," a PSNI
OL,9,Fspokesperson said.
OL,11,F"He managed to escape with his dog
OL,12,Fthrough a window after which he
OL,13,Ftackled the fire using a garden hose
OL,14,Funtil the arrival of the NIFRS.
OL,16,F"This will have been an extremely
OL,17,Fdistressing ordeal for the male
OL,18,Foccupant, and it is sheer fortunate he
OL,19,Fwas able to get out of the property.
