OL,3,CDerry house fire investigated as arson
OL,5,F"This was a reprehensible attack which
OL,6,Fwe're investigating as arson with
OL,7,Fintent to endanger life.
OL,9,F"Enquiries are ongoing to establish
OL,10,Fwho was involved and why this occurred.
OL,12,F"We're appealing to anyone who may
OL,13,Fhave been travelling in this area
OL,14,Faround 3am, or who has information or
OL,15,Frelevant dash cam which may assist our
OL,16,Fenquiries, to call us on 101."
